                                production, distribution and use of such drugs under strict
                                control;

div.p:
It was agreed to invite the following countries to send observers: Italy
                            and the Netherlands to the Commission’s meetings on opium and opiates;
                            Argentina, Bolivia, and Colombia to the meetings on the coca leaf;
                            Lebanon and Pakistan to the meetings on cannabis; Belgium, Israel, Italy
                            and the Netherlands to the meetings on control of other substances,
                            including barbiturates.
